" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 542px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    In-toeing and out-toeing",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 522px; height: 491px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    In-toeing (upper panel) is a rotational variation in which the feet or toes point toward the midline during gait. Out-toeing (lower panel) is a rotational variation in which the feet or toes point away from the midline during gait.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
